room_title: Escape room "Billy's Nightmare" by Omega Escape Room in Buffalo
review: We went to Billy's Nightmare escape room at Omega in Hamburg. It was a ton of fun. Very clever and tricky-- but they do give you some clues which helped our group get out with seconds to spare. The staff was helpful and energetic. Would recommend.
